com.opcoach.training.rental
Interface RentalObject

All Known Implementing Classes:
RentalObjectImpl
public interface RentalObject

A representation of the model object 'Object'.

The following features are supported:

  • ID
  • Name
  • Parent Agency
  • Dispo
